data.description: PRICE REDUCTION 1/21/24! NEW PICS WITHOUT OWNERS BELONGINGS UPLOADED 01/05/24! Get it before it's gone! Gorgeous and charming 2 bedroom 1 bathroom block home nestled in the wonderful and desired neighborhood of Meadowlawn in North Central St. Petersburg. This is an excellent opportunity to purchase a great home in a great neighborhood. This home boasts a beautiful and spacious open floor plan and offers an open living and dining room, as well as a light and bright recently remodeled kitchen with breakfast bar. The gorgeous kitchen offers quartz countertops, a farmhouse sink, bronze hardware, and a lovely backsplash. Both bedrooms are spacious and include gorgeous moldings. The bathroom has been recently updated with porcelain tile and a new vanity. Other recent updates/improvements include; COMPLETELY PAID OFF solar panels that typically keep the power bill under $100 for current owner, interior paint, wood laminate flooring, newer HVAC, water heater, newer windows, newer fiberglass exterior doors, and more! Lots of storage throughout including a storage room off the carport with in unit laundry, and a storage shed in the backyard. Out back the large fenced in yard offers plenty of room for a pool or storage for a trailer or boat. Conveniently located near great schools, Sawgrass Lake Park and MeadowLawn park, golfing, shopping, dining, entertainment, Downtown Tampa and St. Petersburg, with easy access to I-275. All listing info must be verified by buyer/buyers agent.
